f the increase promised by a work of art, depends upon what obstacles are impeding human progress at any given time.<\\/p>\",\"readingPage\":\"9\",\"readingNote\":\"\"}}},\"37\":\"\"}}', '2014-05-23 16:55:16', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'bbc84423-947c-4c85-ab08-9438a58f4d3b');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('119', '401', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Whitman Language\",\"slug\":\"whitman-language\",\"postDate\":1400974551,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Walt Whitman\",\"2\":\"<p>Language, be it remember\\u2019d, is not an abstract construction of the learn\\u2019d, or of dictionary-makers, but is something arising out of the work, needs, ties, joys, affections, tastes, of long generations of humanity, and has its bases broad and low, close to the ground.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:35:51', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'c7a3d577-4ee0-4a83-b4f7-942923b2d7d3');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('120', '402', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Foucault Beginning\",\"slug\":\"foucault-beginning\",\"postDate\":1400974603,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Michel Foucault\",\"2\":\"<p>We are always in the position of beginning again.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:36:43', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'e82064e3-80ba-426b-9e57-89232b9102ae');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('121', '403', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Linji Dependence\",\"slug\":\"linji-dependence\",\"postDate\":1400974640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Linji\",\"2\":\"<p>What I point out to you is only that you shouldn\\u2019t allow yourselves to be confused by others. Act when you need to, without further hesitation or doubt. People today can\\u2019t do this&mdash;what is their affliction? Their affliction is in their lack of self-confidence. If you do not spontaneously trust yourself sufficiently, you will be in a frantic state, pursuing all sorts of objects and being changed by those objects, unable to be independent.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:37:20', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'efb9c034-9c4f-4bfe-a3b4-104ad5780d5b');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('122', '404', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Thoreau Highest of Arts\",\"slug\":\"thoreau-highest-of-arts\",\"postDate\":1400974719,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Henry David Thoreau\",\"2\":\"<p>It is something to be able to paint a particular picture, or to carve a statue, and so to make a few objects beautiful; but it is far more glorious to carve and paint the very atmosphere and medium through which we look, which morally we can do. To affect the quality of the day, that is the highest of arts. Every man is tasked to make his life, even in its details, worthy of contemplation of his most elevated and critical hour.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:38:39', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '9828529a-4343-41ed-8174-2baea754a077');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('123', '405', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Suzuki Do Something New\",\"slug\":\"suzuki-do-something-new\",\"postDate\":1400974769,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Shunryu Suzuki\",\"2\":\"<p>And we should forget, day by day, what we have done; this is true non-attachment. And we should do something new. To do something new, of course we must know our past, and this is alright. But we should not keep holding onto anything we have done; we should only reflect on it. And we must have some idea of what we should do in the future. But the future is the future, the past is the past; now we should work on something new.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:39:29', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '4e5faa04-3623-4143-b7a0-27e5ef982c24');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('124', '406', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Aurelius Formed by Nature\",\"slug\":\"aurelius-formed-by-nature\",\"postDate\":1400974802,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Marcus Aurelius\",\"2\":\"<p>Nothing happens to any man which he is not formed by nature to bear.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-24 23:40:02', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '7f1e12b3-cf84-4e47-a3c6-7f518dd07285');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('125', '407', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"James One and Many\",\"slug\":\"james-one-and-many\",\"postDate\":1401027404,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"William James\",\"2\":\"<p>The notion of the \\u2018one\\u2019 breeds foreigness and that of the \\u2018many\\u2019 intimacy.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:16:44', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'fe2a7cf5-648e-4ebb-b372-ae8b6ac2173a');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('126', '408', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Confucius Heart on the Way\",\"slug\":\"confucius-heart-on-the-way\",\"postDate\":1401027447,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Confucius\",\"2\":\"<p>The Master said, \\u2018I set my heart on the Way, base myself on virtue, lean upon benevolence for support and take my recreation in the arts.\\u2019<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:17:27', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '12425f03-3d57-4bc2-9bbc-49d16ad970a1');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('127', '409', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Epictetus Wisdom and Strength\",\"slug\":\"epictetus-wisdom-and-strength\",\"postDate\":1401027481,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Epictetus\",\"2\":\"<p>Have the wisdom to know what cannot be changed, and the strength to change what can<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:18:01', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '4ffe2641-70b1-4af9-849c-938a1d858845');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('128', '410', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Thoreau Farmer\'s Fields\",\"slug\":\"thoreau-farmers-fields\",\"postDate\":1401027527,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Henry David Thoreau\",\"2\":\"<p>Look at [the farmers\\u2019] fields, and imagine what they might write, if ever they should put pen to paper. Or what they have not written on the face of the earth already, clearing, and burning, and subsoiling, in and in, and out and out, and over and over, again and again, erasing what they had already written for want of parchment.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:18:48', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '95c7c5fe-2314-498d-8c4e-81e176b286cc');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('129', '409', '10', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Epictetus Wisdom and Strength\",\"slug\":\"epictetus-wisdom-and-strength\",\"postDate\":1401027480,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Epictetus\",\"2\":\"<p>Have the wisdom to know what cannot be changed, and the strength to change what can.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:18:58', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '683dba3f-9156-400b-901a-f6eae87fb749');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('130', '411', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Hegel Beauty and Art\",\"slug\":\"hegel-beauty-and-art\",\"postDate\":1401027633,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"G.W.F. Hegel\",\"2\":\"<p>Beauty and art pervade all the business of life like a kindly genius, brightly adorning our surroundings whether interior or exterior, mitigating the seriousness of existence and the complexities of the real life, extinguishing idleness in an entertaining fashion, and, where there is nothing good to be achieved, filling the place of vice better than vice itself.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:20:34', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '7e0a0674-e68f-4dcd-a420-bc5566efc440');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('131', '412', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Sartre un Chat\",\"slug\":\"sartre-un-chat\",\"postDate\":1401027691,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Jean Paul Sartre\",\"2\":\"<p>C\\u2019est rare, un chat qui vous regarde dans le yeux.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:21:31', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '9ae9ab4c-230a-4b30-b965-ecde33c58c83');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('132', '413', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Basho Grass Pillow\",\"slug\":\"basho-grass-pillow\",\"postDate\":1401027742,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Matsuo Basho\",\"2\":\"<p>Together let us eat<\\/p><p>Ears of wheat,&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Sharing at night<\\/p><p>A grass pillow.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:22:22', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '9a04db8a-0cf6-4db2-ae30-bce74924a8e8');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('133', '414', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Po-chang Hungry and Tired\",\"slug\":\"po-chang-hungry-and-tired\",\"postDate\":1401027785,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Po-chang\",\"2\":\"<p>When hungry, eat; when tired, sleep.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:23:05', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'cf335f3e-518a-4fe5-b5ca-d30f72eebb30');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('134', '415', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Hui-neng Dirty Skeletons\",\"slug\":\"hui-neng-dirty-skeletons\",\"postDate\":1401027839,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Hui-neng\",\"2\":\"<p>A living man who sits and does not lie down; A dead man who lies down and does not sit! After all these are just dirty skeletons.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:23:59', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '6cb92ee5-fbd4-491e-baeb-f4d2d245ab40');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('135', '416', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Melville Take My Body\",\"slug\":\"melville-take-my-body\",\"postDate\":1401027936,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Herman Melville\",\"2\":\"<p>Methinks we have hugely mistaken this matter of Life and Death. Methinks that what they call my shadow here on earth is my true substance. Methinks that in looking at things spiritual, we are too much like oysters observing the sun through the water, and thinking that thick water the thinnest of air. Methinks my body is but the lees of my better being. In fact take my body who will, take it I say, it is not me.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:25:36', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', 'db71b4dc-758a-4bd2-8aff-0c7a15000db8');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('136', '417', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"van Gogh Nobody\",\"slug\":\"van-gogh-nobody\",\"postDate\":1401027993,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Vincent van Gogh\",\"2\":\"<p>What am I in most people\\u2019s eyes? A nonentity, or an eccentric and disagreeable man &mdash; somebody who has no position in society and never will have, in short, the lowest of the low. Very well, even if this were true, then I should want my work to show what is in the heart of such an eccentric, of such a nobody.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:26:33', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '31657b12-6a14-456b-ab56-4b42b1fad67b');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('137', '418', '10', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Bringhurst Rules\",\"slug\":\"bringhurst-rules\",\"postDate\":1401028041,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"44\":\"Robert Bringhurst\",\"2\":\"<p>By all means break the rules, and break them beautifully, deliberately, and well.<\\/p>\"}}', '2014-05-25 14:27:21', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '2b05440b-c63d-4b97-b859-35b88afed365');
INSERT INTO `craft_entryversions` (`id`, `entryId`, `sectionId`, `creatorId`, `locale`, `num`, `notes`, `data`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES ('138', '390', '9', '1', 'en_us', '8', NULL, '{\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Selected Essays\",\"slug\":\"berger-selected-essays\",\"postDate\":1400859600,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"42\":\"John Berger\",\"2\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"43\":[\"389\"],\"32\":\"\",\"38\":{\"392\":{\"type\":\"readingQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"readingQuotation\":\"<p>To take a long-term historical view you must stand outside your own time and culture. You must base yourself on the past, in an imaginary future or in the centre of an alternative culture. Your general opinion will probably be right. But you will almost certainly be blind to the processes by which your own period is changing itself. you will tend to see the dramatic break between the culture with which you identify yourself and the culture that surrounds you more clearly than you will see the dialectic leading up to and away from that break.<\\/p>\",\"readingPage\":\"6\",\"readingNote\":\"\"}},\"393\":{\"type\":\"readingQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"readingQuotation\":\"<p>After we have responded to a work of art, we leave it, carrying away in our consciousness something which we didn\'t have before. This something amounts to more than our memory of the incident represented, and also more than our memory of the shapes and colours an spaces which the artist has used and arranged. What we take away with us -- on the most profound level -- is the memory of the artist\'s way of looking at the world.<\\/p>\",\"readingPage\":\"8\",\"readingNote\":\"\"}},\"394\":{\"type\":\"readingQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"readingQuotation\":\"<p>Here it is essential to remember that the specific meaning of a work of art changes -- if it didn\'t, no work could outlive its period, and no agnostic could appreciate a Bellini. The meaning of the improvement, of the increase promised by a work of art, depends upon what obstacles are impeding human progress at any given time.<\\/p>\",\"readingPage\":\"9\",\"readingNote\":\"\"}}},\"37\":\"\"}}', '2014-05-26 03:50:52', '2014-06-04 12:48:57', '5fcbbbb6-500f-4419-ba7a-e6b1941d8434');
