INSERT INTO `craft_searchindex` (`elementId`, `attribute`, `fieldId`, `locale`, `keywords`) VALUES ('730', 'field', '2', 'en_us', ' it s great working in a museum at the brooklyn museum the tech offices are on the sixth and top floor inaccessible to the public anytime my eyes get that computer screen strain i take a fifteen minute break walk the stairs down a floor and wander the galleries art is refreshing i m really surprised i forgot that there really isn t anything like galleries full of paintings sculpture antique furniture images on the web are no substitute when there is nothing artificial between the art and your eyes the connection is physical and you can feel it if for no other reason this is why art museums must exist the brooklyn museum isn t a huge one it s sizable but it s footprint is maybe a quarter that of the metropolitan museum of art and our collection has a much quieter profile than moma still there s a lot of pride here and our stated mission is wonderful the goal of our institution is to be a museum for the local community to be about the visitor not our curators or any biennial nonsense i haven t been able to talk about what i m working on i will soon but we re holding our collective tongues out of respect to our donor who s footing the bill for the whole thing and is yet to make their own announcement it s an exciting project and its good natured and it s attempting something really new i am honored to be a part of it the museum is closed on mondays and tuesdays sometimes the lights are out and the galleries are dimly lit with only security lights walking around with museum like this makes the art somehow more alive as if they re sleeping they have down time too just like us it reminds me that we re all lucky to have this art at our disposal when the lights are on they re here for us what i m working on might even bring people closer to this art it could help them own it a little further to get a little more out of their time visiting with us that s the hope anyway i ve learned to love art again and i hope that this project might bring people closer to it too ');
